environment: Netbeans 8, Spring 4, Hibernate 4, MySQL, Tomcat 7

how to call:
http://localhost:8080/SpringMVCHibernate/contacts

DDL:
on commandline start mysql shell by typing mysql.

create database:
mysql>	CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS MYTEST
	DEFAULT CHARACTER SET utf8
	DEFAULT COLLATE utf8_general_ci;

create user and grant privileges to user:
mysql>	CREATE USER gp@localhost IDENTIFIED BY 'pwd';
mysql>	GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO gp@localhost;

execute setup.sql:
mysql> source setup.sql (creates tables)
